Documentation Tools

Recommended tools for documentation website:

Option 1 – GitHub Pages
	•	Host documentation directly from GitHub
	•	Use Markdown
	•	Free hosting
	•	Easy updates

Option 2 – MkDocs

Documentation generator for technical projects.

Features:
	•	Markdown based
	•	Clean documentation theme
	•	Navigation sidebar
	•	Search
	•	Easy deployment

Option 3 – Docusaurus
	•	Documentation website framework
	•	Versioned docs
	•	Blog support
	•	Good for large projects

