Documentation Principles

NSD documentation should be:
	•	Clear
	•	Technical but understandable
	•	Structured
	•	Version controlled
	•	Public where possible
	•	Security-sensitive information separated
	•	Continuously updated
	•	Accessible to international users (English recommended)

